Products.Name: Saxa Cooking Salt
Products.SupplyLimitMessage: 'Saxa Cooking Salt' has a supply limit of 36. The quantity in your cart has been reduced accordingly. To purchase a larger quantity, please contact us on 1800 000 610. Please note we do not supply trade orders.
Products.RichDescription:
Saxa Cooking Salt is Australia's traditional salt choice for the kitchen. The medium sized crystals can be pinched or measured out and used for all your cooking requirements, dissolving quickly to disperse flavour. It is ideal for crisping crackling and salting water for pasta.
